description:
In this Everything Iconic POP Dive, guest Annabelle DeSisto and I dive into the iconic career of Tyra Banks. Tyra's contributions to society are so vast that this is PART 1 of a 2-part exploration into the life of Tyra. In part 1, we discuss America's Next Top Model ("Be Quiet Tiffany!"), Coyote Ugly, and so much more.
